metadata.name: Sigil II - 01
metadata.description:
Invocation 00 - Sigil 01

Generative | Flexible Algorithm
JS | SVG | JPG | Ink on paper

As a designer, we are trained to master our tools, taking control over our relationship with technology.

Generative methods and random variables introduced into the design process tends to replace mastery with dialogue. This series depicts the outcomes of that dialogue.

Digital: 4000x 4000h px | High Resolution JPG.

Plot: On request you will receive a 420mm x 420mm plot of this artwork (1 of 1).
Generative art using JS.
